Package: ranalyticsplatform
Title: R Analytics Platform — Learning Project
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Author", "", , "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A personal learning project exploring modern R-based data
    engineering patterns. Combines targets pipelines, parquet/Arrow/DuckDB
    data processing, renv reproducibility, and automated Quarto website
    publishing via GitHub Actions. Not a production system — this is an
    educational field notebook.
